Class EntityIdentifierReaderImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityIdentifierReader

    public class EntityIdentifierReaderImpl
extends Object
implements EntityIdentifierReader
    Encapsulates the logic for reading a single entity identifier from a JDBC ResultSet, including support for fetches that are part of the identifier.
